name: Farewell
description:
When something that was always nearby goes away, we can focus on that contour for the first time.

At the same time, we find that the song of grass, the temperature of the breeze at night, and the brilliance of the stars, everything is based on love.
We should live on the basis of love too.
Because it's the precious message that "farewell" tells us.

This art was created to snuggle up to "farewell".
